title: The Uncluded - Hokey Fright (2013) EAC-FLAC
description:
Performers: Aesop Rock & Kimya Dawson

From Wikipedia: Hokey Fright is the only studio album by The Uncluded, a collaboration between rapper Aesop Rock (real name Ian Matthias Bavitz) and anti-folk singer-songwriter Kimya Dawson. It was released on May 7, 2013 on the Rhymesayers Entertainment label. Every part of every song on the album is performed by either Bavitz or Dawson, with the exception of the drums on "Delicate Cycle", which were played by James McNew of Yo La Tengo.
